    *** At ~120k SNPs the control HOLDS but Kotias does NOT break it.
    *** Test 3 requires a high SNP basis. Most published 1240K aDNA
    *** studies work well below 900k. THIS IS A MAJOR LIMITATION AND
    *** MUST BE STATED IN THE ABSTRACT, NOT THE DISCUSSION.

    *** DISCRIMINATION LOST at one or more bases: a LEGITIMATE
    *** reference produces a Kotias-sized fold. Test 3 would then be
    *** reacting to perturbation, not to the violation. Report it.
